                    <li><strong>LLM Optimisation:</strong> Refined prompt architectures and conversational memory frameworks, reducing hallucination rate by ~40% and cutting API token cost by 25% through context compression.</li>
                    <li><strong>AI Voice Agents:</strong> Developed real-time AI voice agents integrated with Twilio and WebSockets, achieving sub-500ms end-to-end response latency for live conversational interactions.</li>
                  </ul>
